lf you have to
drop it in high cover...

365
00:25:13,011 --> 00:25:15,445
- Got him.
- Yeah, you did.

366
00:25:15,514 --> 00:25:17,641
Good shot, son.

367
00:25:23,488 --> 00:25:27,948
John, your mother,
she may be a little crazy,

368
