for us and find out.

389
00:27:44,596 --> 00:27:46,757
You can still
change your mind.

390
00:27:46,831 --> 00:27:49,629
Nah. They already
shaved my back.

391
00:27:53,238 --> 00:27:55,399
l'm so thankful for you.

392
00:27:58,710 --> 00:28:00,371
